{
  "texts": [
    "Thus, many resource-limited healthcare organizations or individual physicians may rely on third-party, external GenAI tools (107).",
    "Given the great utility of GenAI, knowledge workers may be sorely tempted to upload confidential information, despite significant risks (108).",
    "In healthcare, such risks are legal as well as ethical in nature, and transgressions can have implications for professional development.",
    "Though the timeline is uncertain, GenAI technology will continue to advance.",
    "There is little question that GenAI will come to have a key role in the medical education landscape."
  ]
}